      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>General information about display and sample filters in RenderMan: <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542235044/Sample+and+Display+Filters\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542235044\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Sample and Display Filters</a> </p><p>To add a sample of display filter simply add one of the dedicated LOP node to create the corresponding USD filter primitive.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"a98cef59-4446-4f39-b6bb-3436d0b4d8f9\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>The previous ways (either via the dedicated tab on the Render Settings LOP or via the PxrSampleFilter and PxrDisplayFilter LOPs) to add a filter, while still supported, are deprecated.</p></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"samplefilerLOPs.png\" width=\"935\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642120/samplefilerLOPs.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763053663314&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=935&amp;height=574\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642120/samplefilerLOPs.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763053663314&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"574\" data-width=\"935\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"665354290\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"samplefilerLOPs.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642120\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"6\" data-media-id=\"69c58d2e-c163-4ef6-9cc7-455530017287\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642120/samplefilerLOPs.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763053663314&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=935&amp;height=574 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642120/samplefilerLOPs.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763053663314&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=935&amp;height=574 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"displayfilterLOPs.png\" width=\"935\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642120/displayfilterLOPs.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1763053643543&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=935&amp;height=574\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642120/displayfilterLOPs.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1763053643543&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"574\" data-width=\"935\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"665550858\" data-linked-resource-version=\"2\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"displayfilterLOPs.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642120\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"6\" data-media-id=\"5eaaf951-1c42-4ecf-8119-aeb0d20015c1\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642120/displayfilterLOPs.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1763053643543&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=935&amp;height=574 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642120/displayfilterLOPs.png?version=2&amp;modificationDate=1763053643543&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=935&amp;height=574 1x\"></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>Then assign it to the render settings primitive:</p><ul><li><p>Houdini 20.5 and below: use a PxrAssign LOP (or either the PxrAssignSampleFilter or PxrAssignDisplayFilter alias) to assign a filter primitive to a render settings primitive. The render settings primitive must exist before assignment.</p></li><li><p>Houdini 21.0 and above: while the PxrAssign LOP workflow is still valid, it is also possible to assign directly a filter on the Render Settings LOP.</p></li></ul><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"assignFilter.png\" width=\"1249\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642120/assignFilter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763053672494&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1249&amp;height=702\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642120/assignFilter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763053672494&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"706\" data-width=\"1255\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"662798517\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"assignFilter.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642120\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"6\" data-media-id=\"0d2fcb90-464d-41b9-9353-5c57c9212f3a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642120/assignFilter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763053672494&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1255&amp;height=706 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642120/assignFilter.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763053672494&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1249&amp;height=702 1x\"></span><p>If the assignment was properly done, in the Scene Graph, on the Render Settings primitive, the filter primitive should be listed on either ri:sampleFilters or ri:displaytFilters attributes in H21 and above or, on either outputs:ri:sampleFilters or outputs:ri:displayFilters attributes for H20.5 and below.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"filterAssignedH20.5.png\" width=\"917\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642120/filterAssignedH20.5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763053730695&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=917&amp;height=453\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642120/filterAssignedH20.5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763053730695&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"453\" data-width=\"917\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"663617646\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"filterAssignedH20.5.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642120\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"6\" data-media-id=\"505695c5-637c-4aa1-91f3-78d37616979f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642120/filterAssignedH20.5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763053730695&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=917&amp;height=453 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642120/filterAssignedH20.5.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763053730695&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=917&amp;height=453 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"filterAssignedH21.png\" width=\"646\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642120/filterAssignedH21.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763053739348&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=646&amp;height=328\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642120/filterAssignedH21.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763053739348&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"328\" data-width=\"646\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"663617652\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"filterAssignedH21.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642120\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"6\" data-media-id=\"8a7c1b32-a9b9-4af2-b589-0bdf76d5b7f8\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642120/filterAssignedH21.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763053739348&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=646&amp;height=328 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642120/filterAssignedH21.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1763053739348&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=646&amp;height=328 1x\"></span><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
